    public class StandardNodeImpl
extends NodeImpl
implements StandardNode
    An implementation of the model object 'Standard Node'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Traceability Status
    • Operator
    • Label
    • Component Ref
    • Behavior Ref
    • Traceability Link
    • Leaf
    • Parent
